7a35172a344","tid":2164155,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"耶和華係眾數黎<br />\n可能有啲後悔有啲唔後悔<br />\n正因為佢可以同時存在後悔同唔後悔兩個狀態，所以佢全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"耶和華係獨一真神喎"},{"pid":"fed1cf990ea4b7353837a71a6a874497c25e312b","tid":2164155,"uid":286209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d3937a32256c7722c202801f8ee8f157a77e6b","tid":2164155,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78f097b93dc3ddcb41e9c29d38a44b2f5ec7178f","tid":2164155,"uid":286209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"948328d24eaf7219902df03bfcce782f10343fa3","tid":2164155,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"係喇 至叻係你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c512a9c0d9e2afaad5b2fcc41f043170c0b0d8ca","tid":2164155,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"聖經係一個collection<br />\n<br />\n每本書有唔同作者<br />\n<br />\n有矛盾唔出奇"},{"pid":"672d08e8647ae16ab6081e67d1e30de0d429e658","tid":2164155,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d77fa92da4ce7ce73fa1d6a10ebe762e10bcc61","tid":2164155,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"//基督徒回應這些矛盾，大致上有這些說法： 2.聖經中的字並不是字面的意思//<br />\n<br />\n//這就來到第二點的問題，預先假定了聖經沒有矛盾，所以所有矛盾的地方都不是字面的意思，因此聖經沒有矛盾。這樣的說法就等於：因為聖經絕對無誤，所以聖經絕對無誤。這叫做循環論證，是一個嚴重的邏輯謬誤。//<br />\n<br />\n其實依點講得幾中 <br />\n但係，文章無提到一點：相信聖經「內在結構」無矛盾有一個前提，就係<span class=\"red\"><strong>你信基督教</strong></span>，退一步講就係「從基督教既觀點理解」。<br />\n<br />\n「聖經本文有無矛盾」同「基督教既教義有無矛盾」係兩回事。而且係信仰上，「信神」一定係先於「信聖經」的。<br />\n<br />\n係依個前提下，處理經文之間既矛盾先有意義。例如各段落背後有不同既語境，唔同程度既行為有唔同程度既結果。矛盾之間又反映到乜野既信條。<br />\n<br />\n至於你問基督徒點解信耶穌，依度就唔係理性可以解釋既問題了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS1:其實無邊個讀過神學既人真係會戇鳩到覺得聖經真係完美得不可反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SQJXqkggWsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSQJXqkggWsU&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInJ0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=78fe21a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SQJXqkggWsU</a>"},{"pid":"1aa308e28d4c136b01a06d0f53435b991e456633","tid":2164155,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d2b49076aa6114e61254da6112c45026afb3bc","tid":2164155,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af7d8bde26df74cf148c5f84f41c07a35172a344","tid":2164155,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"耶和華係眾數黎<br />\n可能有啲後悔有啲唔後悔<br />\n正因為佢可以同時存在後悔同唔後悔兩個狀態，所以佢全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"耶和華係獨一真神喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"舊約希伯來文聖經係用複數<br />\nElohim"},{"pid":"2b4c79a5def74969fee45fbec5b5bca002af8c52","tid":2164155,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c512a9c0d9e2afaad5b2fcc41f043170c0b0d8ca","tid":2164155,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"聖經係一個collection<br />\n<br />\n每本書有唔同作者<br />\n<br />\n有矛盾唔出奇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"但係聖經都是神所默示的<br />\n神唔會錯，也唔會有矛盾"},{"pid":"18f4c00fc25f07408b84ac6b18470ad608c3a6e4","tid":2164155,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score